<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>Linux - 标签 - w23ta0's blog</title><link>https://w23ta0.github.io/tags/linux/</link><description>This is my new Hugo FixIt site</description><generator>Hugo 0.145.0 &amp; FixIt v0.3.16</generator><language>zh-cn</language><managingEditor>tom920wt@hotmail.com (w23ta0)</managingEditor><webMaster>tom920wt@hotmail.com (w23ta0)</webMaster><lastBuildDate>Fri, 07 Mar 2025 11:36:22 +0000</lastBuildDate><atom:link href="https://w23ta0.github.io/tags/linux/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>在KVM虚拟机中安装Android-x86模拟器</title><link>https://w23ta0.github.io/posts/20220510-%E5%9C%A8kvm%E8%99%9A%E6%8B%9F%E6%9C%BA%E4%B8%AD%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85%E5%AE%89%E5%8D%93x86%E6%A8%A1%E6%8B%9F%E5%99%A8/</link><pubDate>Tue, 10 May 2022 16:02:55 +0000</pubDate><author>tom920wt@hotmail.com (w23ta0)</author><guid>https://w23ta0.github.io/posts/20220510-%E5%9C%A8kvm%E8%99%9A%E6%8B%9F%E6%9C%BA%E4%B8%AD%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85%E5%AE%89%E5%8D%93x86%E6%A8%A1%E6%8B%9F%E5%99%A8/</guid><category domain="https://w23ta0.github.io/categories/android/">Android</category><description>&lt;h2 id="准备android-x86的iso镜像" class="heading-element">&lt;span>准备Android-x86的iso镜像&lt;/span>
 &lt;a href="#%e5%87%86%e5%a4%87android-x86%e7%9a%84iso%e9%95%9c%e5%83%8f" class="heading-mark">
